fields.name: processName
fields.label: Process Name
fields.referenceRule: select NAME, NAME AS TXT, DESCRIPTION from WF_PROCESSDEFINITION  WHERE CLASS = 'P' AND STATUS = 'Active'

fields.name: processVersion
fields.label: Process Version
fields.referenceRule: select VERSION, VERSION AS TXT, NAME, DESCRIPTION from WF_PROCESSDEFINITION  WHERE CLASS = 'P' AND NAME = :processName
